Text:
TY Shuz :) 
               Wouldn't be able to get through my boring ass job without your goodness :) Glad they pay me well.

I read one of your posts a few weeks ago. You said there's 50+ downloads and nobody says thanks. You're right dude, so I signed up for the sole purpose of saying thanks to the very dedicated Mr. Shuazien. I've been using this site since the 30 day suspension in June 3 years ago. I subscribe to XM in 2 of my cars, but my hours are fucked up, so you come through day after day for me. Shit; sometimes the show ends 10:45am and the 64K MP3 is up at 12:15. Keep it up, thanks for everything, and for those of you who download, Say thanks to SHU and Mother Goose as Well. 
SNIPER
